---
/**
 * Slide 09 · Close — opinion is the product. Echoes the cover.
 */
---

<section data-slot="09" data-variant="fjd-v1" class="deck-section deck-glow" style="justify-content: center;">
  <span class="deck-kicker">09 / 09</span>

  <div class="max-w-5xl">
    <p class="deck-eyebrow mb-5" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Close</p>
    <h2 class="deck-h1">
      Opinion is <span class="deck-gradient">the product.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="deck-lede mt-7" style="max-width: 64ch;">
      Design backward from the job. Build for frontier demand. Pick the fields that
      clear demand × employer pull × apprenticeship fit — and say no to the rest.
    </p>

    <div class="deck-rule mt-8 mb-8" style="max-width: 14rem;"></div>

    <p class="deck-lede" style="max-width: 58ch; color: var(--color-text); font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.7rem);">
      A program for everyone serves no employer well. So build one that does.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
